{
  "stem": "3085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were-- there were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there were instances when there were fights and-- in that school, when we were harassed by other students because of being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I recall one instance when we were studying history.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And our teacher was actually talking about-- I, I think it was the, the, the Roman conquest of Jerusalem in AD 67, and mentioned that, at that point, the Jews were all dispersed around the world as a result of the Roman conquest.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of the kids in, in, in the class made a loud comment, saying, 'unfortunately.' And the teacher responded, [BACKGROUND NOISE] I'm not interested in anybody's opinion.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in that regard, the teacher was, you know, quite-- I appreciated that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, some.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think they were very close to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, yes, we were friendly with some of them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some, as I say, again, just like with the teachers, some of the students were quite, quite sympathetic to us and friendly.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And others were not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there's another-- a point, of course, here to mention is that some of the students were actually non-Catholic but non-Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had Protestant-- a few Protestant kids in the class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were treated sometimes as badly, or almost as badly, as the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, again, history class when they were taught-- when the priest was teaching about Reformation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Those, those kids were-- they were uncomfortable because, obviously, the Reformation was taught from the point of view of the Catholic church.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And those Protestant children were not very comfortable in class.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it wasn't just the Jews, but some of the Protestants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There weren't too many-- I think there were a couple of Protestants in the class, one Calvinist and one Lutheran.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- so it wasn't just us.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
